text: Hervé Lougoundji (born 27 April 1975) is a football manager from Central African Republic who currently not contracted by a club or national team. From May 2012 to August 2014 he coached the Central African Republic national football team.Profile at Soccerpunter.com == References == ==External links== *Profile at Soccerway.com Category:Living people Category:Central African Republic football managers Category:Central African Republic national football team managers Category:1975 births
